OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowery rain
OL,6,Fedging eastwards this evening, giving
OL,7,Foccasional heavier bursts, but perhaps
OL,8,Fremaining dry in some eastern areas.
OL,9,FOften dry through the early hours but
OL,10,Fsome rain or drizzle is likely over
OL,11,Fhigher ground. Turning breezier and
OL,12,Fstaying very mild.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FOften cloudy with some
OL,15,Fdrizzle in places first thing. Heavier
OL,16,Fand more persistent rain arriving in
OL,17,Fthe west through the afternoon.
OL,18,FTurning windier with gales possible in
OL,19,Fthe northwest. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
