OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FUnsettled
OL,6,Fon Friday with coastal gales possible
OL,7,Fand showers or longer spells of rain.
OL,8,FFine on Saturday with lighter winds,
OL,9,Fthen wet and windy again on Sunday.
OL,10,FStaying mild.
